Package project4

Class DateTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • project4.DateTime

  • public class DateTime
extends java.lang.Object
    DateTime is able to store and return dates and times. These can be manually set or automatically set to the current date and time. T The date, time, or both can also be printed out.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Hunter Kimbrell
